## Why This Is Asked

This question probes a candidate's ability to design a robust, privacy-preserving streaming system with practical API design, data modeling, and real-world constraints (late arrivals, auditing, fault tolerance).

## Key Concepts

- Secure aggregation in streaming systems
- Tamper-evident append-only logging
- Late-arrival handling and fault tolerance
- Differential privacy budgeting in continuous streams
- API design for edge-device contributions

## Code Example

