## Why This Is Asked
Tests ability to design a cross-region, multi-vendor aggregation pipeline with tamper-evident auditing and model_versioning. It checks API design, data modeling, robust aggregation, and rollout/rollback in production.

## Key Concepts
- Cross-region data ingestion and weighting
- Poisoning resistance and drift detection
- Versioning, canary rollouts, rollback
- Auditability and security controls

## Code Example
```javascript
function trimmedMean(arr, trim=0.1){
  const sorted = arr.slice().sort((a,b)=>a-b);
  const n = sorted.length;
  const k = Math.floor(n * trim);
  const sliced = sorted.slice(k, n - k);
  return sliced.reduce((a,b)=>a+b,0) / sliced.length;
}
```

