- Deterministic scoring: gating should not introduce nondeterminism.
- Validation & observability: log gating decisions for audits.

## Code Example
```javascript
// Pseudo-code: apply feature gating before scoring
function computeScoreWithGating(allFeatures, allowedFeatures){
  const mask = new Set(allowedFeatures || allFeatures.map(f => f.name));
  const included = allFeatures.filter(f => mask.has(f.name));
  return computeScoreFromFeatures(included);
}
```

