## Code Example

```javascript
// Idempotent batch apply
function applyBatch(state, batch) {
  if (state.seenBatches.has(batch.batch_id)) return state;
  state.seenBatches.add(batch.batch_id);
  const total = state.total * state.count + batch.score;
  state.count += 1;
  state.total = total;
  state.globalScore = state.total / state.count;
  return state;
}
```

## Follow-up Questions

